27:46.270 --> 27:46.920
Tá.

27:48.510 --> 27:49.200
Tá.

27:50.880 --> 27:51.510
Tá.

27:54.110 --> 27:55.440
Sim, se houver alguma notícia,

27:55.440 --> 27:56.880
