29:21.830 --> 29:22.680
Venha, sente-se.

29:25.790 --> 29:26.310
Aqui, sente-se.

29:27.030 --> 29:27.750
Por favor, sente-se.

29:30.750 --> 29:31.400
Du Zhaohui,

29:32.150 --> 29:34.240
